Deepak Limbu (Nepali: दिपक लिम्बु): (born 4 May 1983 ) is a playback singer and winner of the first season of Nepali Tara of Nepal. He has done playback singing for more than one thousand nepali songs.
He performed on a worldwide tour and won several musical awards from 2005-2016.
National Film Award 2009- Best playback singer
